title: Southwest Airlines computer outage leaves passengers waiting in long lines
text: LOS ANGELES >> Southwest Airlines passengers were in a long line at Los Angeles International Airport today, as a nationwide computer failure forced agents to issue handwritten tickets for all departing flights. Airport police tweeted out a photo of a huge line in Terminal 1, and said the problem was duplicated elsewhere. Advertisement
